\f0\b Rockbox
\f1\b0  firmware.\
First, we need to download the ready-made theme. I am using the 
\f0\b iPodOS Theme Made by @churbum
\f1\b0 . It contains four main 
\f0\b directories
\f1\b0  (folders):\
