\f2\fs26 wps
\f1\fs24  
\f0\b directory
\f1\b0  contains: a. The 
\f0\b directory
\f1\b0  
\f2\fs26 iPodOS
\f1\fs24  \'96 (the name of the theme). Inside this 
\f0\b directory
\f1\b0  are files with the 
\f0\b .bmp
\f1\b0  extension. These are various icons and background images. b. A file with the 
\f0\b .wps
\f1\b0  extension \'96 this is the code (the Now Playing screen script).\
\pard\pardeftab720\sa280\partightenfactor0

